rows.label: qst201321_msg0001
rows.name:
Where were you trying to
take these children?

rows.label: qst201321_msg0003
rows.name:
Silence will not do you any good now.
Where were you taking them?

rows.label: qst201321_msg0005
rows.name:
We were told to bring children
from nations around the world.

rows.label: qst201321_msg0006
rows.name:
Told to? Then there are more
people involved in this?

rows.label: qst201321_msg0007
rows.name:
Well, of course there are.
You think we could kidnap children
from all around the world on our own?

rows.label: qst201321_msg0011
rows.name: Then let me rephrase my question.

rows.label: qst201321_msg0012
rows.name:
For what purpose were you
abducting these children?

rows.label: qst201321_msg0014
rows.name:
We were just doing it for the
payment our client offered.

rows.label: qst201321_msg0015
rows.name:
It's none of our business what
they wanted with a bunch of brats.

rows.label: qst201321_msg0010
rows.name:
Come on. We'll just have to head
for Port Anangham in Superbia
and investigate there.
